OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,FJersey Electricity have shelved plans
OL,7,Fto build the island's biggest solar
OL,8,Ffarm in St Mary.
OL,10,FThe company proposed installing 9,000
OL,11,Fsolar panels across 22 acres and eight
OL,12,Ffields at Champs Verts in St Mary, but
OL,13,Fthe site's planning application was
OL,14,Ftemporarily withdrawn in February 2025.
OL,16,FThe site would have been almost twice
OL,17,Fthe size of Jersey's next-biggest
OL,18,Fsolar farms at Rue du Moulin a Vent in
OL,19,FSt Clement (four fields, 12 acres) and
OL,20,FSorel on the north coast (eight
OL,21,Ffields, 12 acres).
OL,26,@zD@^qp
