OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,FNow the electricity company has
OL,7,Freleased a statement saying the
OL,8,Fproject is "under review" as part of a
OL,9,Fwider reassessment of its 'Solar 5000'
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FJersey Electricity's statement reads:
OL,13,F"The overall programme is modest in
OL,14,Fscale. If delivered in full, it would
OL,15,Faccount for around 0.6% of the
OL,16,FIsland's available agricultural land,
OL,17,Fwith schemes designed to allow
OL,18,Fcontinued agricultural use, such as
OL,19,Fsheep grazing and other new crop
OL,20,Fopportunities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
