OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,F"Solar generation remains an important
OL,7,Fpart of improving the resilience and
OL,8,Fdiversity of Jersey's electricity
OL,9,Fsupply.
OL,11,F"Local solar generation can help
OL,12,Freduce daytime peak demand,
OL,13,Fparticularly during the summer months,
OL,14,Fwhile providing a stable long-term
OL,15,Ffixed-cost source of energy."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
