OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,FThis is the second wind farm site
OL,7,FJersey Electricity (JE) has shelved in
OL,8,Fas many months, after plans for a
OL,9,Fsolar farm at St Martin's Belle
OL,10,FFontaine site were put on ice in
OL,11,FFebruary.
OL,13,FWilliam Layzell, who leads the
OL,14,Fcampaign group Save This View,
OL,15,Fbelieves that their opposition and
OL,16,Fconcerns from residents were partly
OL,17,Fresponsible for the St Mary's planning
OL,18,Fapplication being initially withdrawn
OL,19,Fmore than a year ago.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
