OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,F"Residents now deserve to be told if
OL,7,FJersey Electricity intends to go ahead
OL,8,For if this scheme, like the one in St
OL,9,FMartin, is to be abandoned," William
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement. "No doubt these
OL,11,Fare questions which will be asked
OL,12,Fduring the election campaign in May.
OL,14,F"Candidates and States Members will
OL,15,Fwant to know how much JE has spent on
OL,16,Fthese two schemes: one scrapped, the
OL,17,Fother unlikely to go ahead."
OL,19,FSave This View has questioned the
OL,20,Fcompany's desire for greater energy
OL,21,Fdiversity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
