OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1773846666
OL,3,CJersey Electricity shelves plans for
OL,4,Cisland's largest solar farm
OL,6,FThey claim that Jersey currently
OL,7,Fimports 95% of its energy from France,
OL,8,Fdelivered through hydroelectric and
OL,9,Fnuclear sources, which are low-carbon.
OL,10,FLa Collette incinerator supplies the
OL,11,Fremaining 5%.
OL,13,FThe States of Jersey are set to debate
OL,14,Fwhether there should be a prohibition
OL,15,Fon solar ground mounts on agricultural
OL,16,Fland.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
